<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ title }} | BEL WORKS</title>
    <meta name="description" content="{{ description }}">
    
    {# Tailwind CSS CDN #}
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>

    {# Google Fonts #}
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;700&family=Source+Serif+4:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <script>
        // Tailwind CSSのカスタム設定
        // デザインディレクションに基づいた設定をここに記述します
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    fontFamily: {
                        sans: ['Inter', 'sans-serif'],
                        serif: ['Source Serif 4', 'serif'],
                    },
                    colors: {
                        'blueprint-black': '#1A1A1A',
                        'concrete-gray': '#F2F2F2',
                        'signal-blue': '#0057FF',
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body class="bg-white text-blueprint-black font-serif">
    
    <!-- Header: Organism -->
    <header class="bg-white shadow-md sticky top-0 z-50">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
            <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-bold font-sans text-blueprint-black">BEL WORKS</a>
            <nav class="hidden md:flex items-center space-x-8">
                <a href="/services" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-signal-blue transition-colors">事業内容</a>
                <a href="/case-studies" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-signal-blue transition-colors">実績</a>
                <a href="/blog" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-signal-blue transition-colors">ブログ</a>
                <a href="/contact" class="bg-signal-blue text-white font-bold py-2 px-5 rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">お問い合わせ</a>
            </nav>
            <button class="md:hidden text-gray-600">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16m-7 6h7"></path></svg>
            </button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        {% block content %}{% endblock %}
    </main>

    <!-- Footer: Organism -->
    <footer class="bg-blueprint-black text-white">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center md:text-left">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 font-sans">BEL WORKS</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">守りの法務から、売上を創る攻めの法務戦略へ。</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 font-sans">サイトマップ</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-2">
                        <li><a href="/services" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">事業内容</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/case-studies" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">実績</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/blog" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">ブログ</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">プライバシーポリシー</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4 font-sans">お問い合わせ</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">プロジェクトのご相談は、<a href="/contact" class="text-signal-blue hover:underline">お問い合わせフォーム</a>からお気軽にどうぞ。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-12 border-t border-gray-700 pt-8 text-center text-gray-500">
                <p>&copy; 2025 BEL WORKS. All Rights Reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
